data.name: Crusher Run
data.desc: If a face-up EARTH Machine monster(s) you control is destroyed by battle or card effect: You can target 1 card on the field; destroy it. You can banish this card from your GY; Set 1 "Outrigger Extension" or "Spin Turn" from your Deck or GY. You can only use each effect of "Crusher Run" once per turn.

card_sets.set_name: 2020 Tin of Lost Memories Mega Pack
